218
00:07:58.935 --> 00:08:01.735
¿Acaso he buscado yendo a verla ganar tiempo,

219
00:08:02.080 --> 00:08:04.320
retardar un momento el instante fatal?

220
00:08:04.800 --> 00:08:06.480
Y me he atrevido a soñar con altos

221
00:08:06.480 --> 00:08:07.120
destinos,

222
00:08:07.440 --> 00:08:09.040
